      <title>天然气价格上涨导致道达尔能源利润下降幅度超过预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-profit-drops-more-than-expected-on-gas-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道达尔能源公司 (TotalEnergies SE) 公布第二季度利润降幅超预期，因为天然气价格下跌和炼油利润率下降抵消了石油价格上涨的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-profit-drops-more-than-expected-on-gas-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:11:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
